query:
UPDATE customer_recommendations
             SET full_name = $1,
                 phone_number_enc = $2,
                 phone_number_nonce = $3,
                 phone_number_hash = $4,
                 city_enc = $5,
                 city_nonce = $6,
                 referral_name = $7,
                 created_by = $8
             WHERE uuid = $9
